{
  "stem": "20800.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So I went to one place where it was [NON-ENGLISH], and they used to do oil from-- from sunflower, sunflower oil.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "To make the oil, you have to beat with the special thing on the seeds to make them-- how you call-- soft.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And get oil out of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And for this I usually get a whole bucket of sunflower seeds.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "That was nice.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Now for many, many days we ate only sunflower seeds.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But we survived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "It was very filling.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And we couldn't feel hunger after we ate that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I remember like-- there was not far a sort of-- not river, but a stream.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "We used to go there and get some water.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And there, because nobody was around, mom went with me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And I remember like now, and she was sitting there, poor thing, [SOBBING] telling me if we have been in Palestine, we wouldn't have it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And I look at her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And I couldn't believe the words she said.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "See, my mother was not a Zionist.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "She was a Jew, with bone and blood.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "She was, remember Palestine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "She said, if we would have been in Palestine, we wouldn't have to go through this whole thing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "But that's not all.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Then they start to come in, people around.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And said, it was not far from this little town.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And in this-- and this town start to-- people start to come, and telling us, there is a sign, all Jews has to come to this place to register.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "no, Nikolaevka, Nikolaevka.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we-- and when we heard that-- they-- they-- they were asking us for documents.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But when we ran from there, [POINTING] from the German with the gun, we throw out all our documents.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't have a thing left.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
